        <item>
            <title>Pagani Imola Roadster 亮相　最強開蓬超跑全球限量 8 部</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/25/pagani-imola-roadster/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=pagani-imola-roadster</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/11/25/pagani-imola-roadster/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[藍骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 25 Nov 2023 14:55:05 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[車壇動向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Pagani Imola Roadster]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超級跑車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1206893</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>超級跑車不是人人買得起，不過只看照片也仍然是賞心悅目。最近 Pagani 就公佈了全新的 Imola Roadster，是目前 Pagani 最強勁的開蓬跑車。<br /><span id="more-1206893"></span></p><p>新的 Imola Roadster 是 Pagani 旗下 Grandi Complicazioni 的最新作品，靈感來自 Huayra R，將 Huayra Roadster BC 的先進科技與空氣動力學結合，在動力和結構上都算是爐火純青。</p><p><img decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="2560" height="1708" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1206894" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-scaled.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-03-HD-1536x1025.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>Imola Roadster 採用瞭大量複合材質，的重量僅為 1,260 公斤，配備了由 Mercedes-Benz AMG 專為 Pagani 設計的 5,980 cc V12 引擎，提供 850 馬力和 1,100 牛米的扭矩。為了駕馭強勁的輸出，Imola Roadster 擁有擴大的前進氣口和雙溫熱空氣出口提升冷卻性能，也是 Pagani 首次將進氣口和後翼支架整合到引擎蓋中，可以提升 V12 的吸氣效果和車輛穩定性。尾燈的新設計和新的空氣通風口則增強後剎車的冷卻效果，同時增加下壓力至高達 600 公斤（在 280km/h 速度下行駛時）。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-scaled.jpg" alt="" width="2560" height="1708" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1206896" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-scaled.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-1280x854.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/Render-Pagani-Imola-Roadster-01-HD-1536x1025.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 770px" /></p><p>Imola Roadster 只會限量生產 8 部，而且一如以往會提供「不限範圍」的自訂服務，每部車都是獨一無二，不過售價方面就未有公佈。</p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.pagani.com/press/pagani-imola-roadster/">Pagani</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div>

